oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph of "Battery B" Veterans Club
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The photo shows men in suits and ties gathered in a formal dining room. The front rank is seated at the table while a second rank stands. A handwritten number in red ink appears on or near each man. These are veterans of Co. B, 114th F.A. Regt., 30th Div. On the reverse, in the same ink, is a numbered list of names that identify each man. Some are honorary members. At the head of the list is the title ""Battery. B Veterans Club --Feb. 26, 1966."
